<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Drop Participation Update</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8edea 0%, #fed6e3 100%); color: #333; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .info-box { background: #f5f5f5; border-left: 4px solid #a8edea; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: #a8edea; color: #333; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ“¢ Drop Update</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for your participation in the <strong>"{{theme}}"</strong> product drop. We wanted to let you know about the selection results.</p>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <strong>Drop Information:</strong><br>
        <strong>Theme:</strong> {{theme}}<br>
        <strong>Total Submissions:</strong> {{totalSubmissions}}<br>
        <strong>Selected Pieces:</strong> {{totalSelected}}<br>
        <strong>Release Date:</strong> {{releaseDate}}
      </div>
      
      <p>While your design didn't make the final selection this time, we want to thank you for your creativity and effort. We received many incredible submissions, and the selection process was highly competitive.</p>
      
      <p><strong>Don't Be Discouraged!</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Future drops will have different themes and aesthetics</li>
        <li>Your work may be perfect for an upcoming drop</li>
        <li>Each submission helps us understand your style better</li>
        <li>We'd love to see you participate in future opportunities</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Keep creating amazing work! Your unique perspective is valuable to our community.</p>
      
      <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="cta-button">{{actionLabel}}</a>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666;">
        Interested in future opportunities? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Engel Fine Design. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
